parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty seat belt buckle can lead to the inability to properly secure oneself, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle is jammed
the male end cannot be inserted into the female end
the buckle will not click
the seat belt cannot be properly secured.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cylinder head failure can cause engine misfires, rough idling, and loss of power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded. In severe cases, it can also cause engine fires.
symptoms: Engine check light illuminates
engine misfires
rough idling
loss of power
hesitation in shifting
smoke or flames coming from under the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt connector can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to a significant safety hazard, especially in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The metal seat belt connector frays or breaks into two pieces
compromising the integrity of the seat belt system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heater blower motor can cause reduced visibility due to fogging or misting of the windshield, leading to potential accidents, especially in low-visibility conditions.
symptoms: The heater blower motor squeaks and stops running
causing visibility issues and discomfort.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure to Engage or Shift
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission to engage or shift can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park or neutral, making it impossible to drive, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle will not come out of park
the transmission will not shift into gear
the vehicle is unable to move
the transmission makes unusual noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission ECM can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to issues with shifting, engagement, and overall vehicle operation, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission will not shift into gear
the vehicle is unable to move
the transmission makes unusual noises or vibrations
the vehicle's dashboard warning lights illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of adequate warranty coverage and poor service from dealerships can lead to frustration, financial burden, and a sense of abandonment for vehicle owners, which can affect their overall trust in the manufacturer and the automotive industry.
symptoms: Denial of warranty claims
lack of assistance from dealerships
inadequate repair attempts
poor communication from manufacturers and dealerships.
